      "content": "You're saying the residents are too \"uninformed\" or \"irrational\" to have a say in how their own streets are changing? That sounds like you're basically saying their input doesn't matter because of who they are. If we switch to this new model, isn't there a risk that the city's economic stability will just fall apart because we aren't following your \"cold, hard numbers\" anymore?",
